f = Figure(resolution = (600, 400))     
ax = list(4)
l = reshape(1:4, 2, 2)
for j = 1:2
    for k = 1:2
        zl = l[j, k]
        ax[zl] = Axis(f[j, k],
            xlabel = string("PC", zl), ylabel = string("PC", zl + 1))
        scatter!(ax[zl], T[:, zl:(zl + 1)];
            color = (:red, .5))
    end
end
